{"tid":1986364,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"估下政府想點玩鳩班考生","createTime":"2020-04-23T19:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T05:47:10.000Z","uid":68483,"like":9,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"19193885f08c08321efb547eeb67f3e11908ef75","tid":1986364,"uid":68483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T19:59:58.000Z","msg":"基本上政府肯定將高年級中學生打做黑五類，今年堅持考DSE明顯係想玩鳩佢地。<br />\n<br />\n依家聯想到嘅賤招有：<br />\n1. 直接混啲肺炎人士入去，死一大批學生<br />\n2. 想你係去考場途中迫地鐵，中招死<br />\n3. 考完之後話在場人士有肺炎，要你隔離14日，唔俾你考埋其他科（仲衰過全科唔考）<br />\n4. 係你考前考後其他時間捉你違反限聚令，直接俾告票你，例如你早到考場溫書就捉鳩你。"},{"pid":"b00281c5d86273e3b8d1029e9f7d0ed9bd6a6206","tid":1986364,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T20:01:15.000Z","msg":"叫藍絲塞尻你鐵？"},{"pid":"dad5570946e84a72a7b3e0c969ed5ad2128a13c0","tid":1986364,"uid":107842,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T20:02:09.000Z","msg":"唔好俾班壓力班DSE考生啦 俾佢地專心左先啦<br />\n<br />\n佢地都會睇連登"},{"pid":"a8d6cc8b7f423a5ffd52a1bda9c3544ab03b8366","tid":1986364,"uid":198035,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T20:02:19.000Z","msg":"唔好咁痴線啦"},{"pid":"d6ecf47de805060385d8921855fd09b555438d55","tid":1986364,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T20:10:45.000Z","msg":"教育部：考完晒DSE理得你班學生要用幾多時間去醫"},{"pid":"5b837e214a02965ff51d28d1e6e5d0d918263659","tid":1986364,"uid":299276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T20:11:11.000Z","msg":"覺得第四最有可能"},{"pid":"b6ce580e3160fc2d05a2b834ac845c6c4d686391","tid":1986364,"uid":75823,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T20:11:33.000Z","msg":"On撚9"},{"pid":"2063c68f67553b63cb188f8ba78ec0d2787b14de","tid":1986364,"uid":75823,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T20:11:53.000Z","msg":"反政府反上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28885699cc4d24e5cdd05720952622f471199188","tid":1986364,"ui